{"id":233015,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-拆迁户集体请求信息公开，南通警方非法/","date":"2012-06-19T15:16:16Z","modified":"2012-06-19T15:16:16Z","title":"维权网 | 拆迁户集体请求信息公开，南通警方非法传唤受害人","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div> </div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日下午</span><span>，南通拆迁受害人严晓燕、邵德云、葛佳声、姜桂芳等三十多人到南通市政府政务中心请求公开有关征地批文及其补偿使用情况的政府信息。当地派出所竟然在没有传唤证的情况下，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日晚间到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日，陆续对政府信息申请人进行传唤。其中，只有周叶拿到传唤证，其余人没有拿到传唤证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>南通当地政府在拆迁过程中，强迫拆迁户签订空白拆迁协议。拆迁户完全有理由怀疑当地政府官员中饱私囊，故集体要求政府信息公开。这恼怒了当地政府官员，竟然以“扰乱单位秩序”为由，一一传唤政府信息公开的申请人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>直到本网发稿时止，姜桂芳等人还在当地派出所被传唤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>受害人的手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>       </span></span></div>\n<div><span>叶炳华：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13382347172</span></div>\n<div><span>葛佳声：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13222190690</span></div>\n<div><span>周叶：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15996630898</span></div>\n<div><span>严晓燕：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18962994796189</span></div>\n<div><span>邵德云：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18906292091</span></div>\n<div><span>姜桂芳：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18921466102</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2882724958953517283?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;